<mvt:comment>Fitment Confirmation V2 partial. Uses existing sd2v2_garage localStorage contract through JS copy enhancement.</mvt:comment>
<section class="sd2-v2-fitment-confirm" aria-label="Vehicle fitment">
	<p class="sd2-kicker">Garage Fitment</p>
	<h2>Confirm This Part Against Your Build</h2>
	<p data-v2-fitment-copy>No vehicle selected. Open Garage to verify year, make, model, and engine before ordering.</p>
	<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--secondary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Open Garage</button>
</section>
